    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此试用版将包含玩家从出生到三岁的历程，总可游玩时间约一个小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到卡牌人生的世界。在这个世界中，你可以通过堆叠卡牌来合成更好的卡牌，获得更好的属性，达成更好的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如，将“灵感”卡牌拖至“眼泪”顶部将会生成“数数”卡牌，数数卡牌能帮助您获得更多的属性！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集卡牌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中将有300+ 张可收集的卡牌，卡牌可以相互合成，也可以售出获得金币，并在商店购买新的卡牌或卡包。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >养成人生与多结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将使用骰子以推进您的人生，提高您的属性以达成不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/a628f4d47784dd1a63d61347f1a3115c.poster.avif?t=1735816200\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/a628f4d47784dd1a63d61347f1a3115c.webm?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/a628f4d47784dd1a63d61347f1a3115c.mp4?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的NPC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中含有丰富的陪伴您成长的NPC以及可攻略的恋爱NPC，丰满的人设背景一定能给您带来不一样的体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗与物品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在异世界中与魔物战斗，装备卡牌以增强属性，消耗卡牌以恢复状态，还可以收复不同的怪物来辅助战斗。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/244c1b1267e7e464edc2fce49435bf2a.poster.avif?t=1735816200\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/244c1b1267e7e464edc2fce49435bf2a.webm?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/244c1b1267e7e464edc2fce49435bf2a.mp4?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/b764d8620b85796aacbd28b92e6e4a24.poster.avif?t=1735816200\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/b764d8620b85796aacbd28b92e6e4a24.webm?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/b764d8620b85796aacbd28b92e6e4a24.mp4?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/c7a6cf222808b4e41a98b9d76605f435.poster.avif?t=1735816200\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/c7a6cf222808b4e41a98b9d76605f435.webm?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/c7a6cf222808b4e41a98b9d76605f435.mp4?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >节日小游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逢年过节都会有独特机制的小游戏供您体验。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/b857dca52f7493122041bdac967c1a3c.poster.avif?t=1735816200\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/b857dca52f7493122041bdac967c1a3c.webm?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300650/extras/b857dca52f7493122041bdac967c1a3c.mp4?t=1735816200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>特点</u></strong> �</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🃏 300+ 张可收集的卡牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 100+个可合成的配方</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ 50+ 个可游玩的活动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 20+ 个不同的可购买的卡包</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕒 7-9 小时的游戏时间</p></li></ul>",
